{"tid":1466612,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"停止分化 停止分化","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:49:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:55:55.000Z","uid":303858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"51814c5912d41029c70c8f8513cec78ee693f30c","tid":1466612,"uid":303858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:49:36.000Z","msg":"今晚捉鬼件事，成功分化到一批唔認同私刑，同埋另一批支持打柒公安嘅人<br />\n<br />\n今晚嘅事係咪鬼都好，我點都唔割<br />\n<br />\n但係往後要認真反思，到底係咪過咗火<br />\n日後佔機場冇問題，但係係咪要維持番和理非，盡量唔影響到旅客？<br />\n<br />\n最後想引番天琦嘅說話：「<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>懇請你們不要被仇恨支配自己，在危難中，仍要時刻保持警覺與思考。</strong></span>」"},{"pid":"bb42ef0ee64c4ccff20b196baf9ef474264bc49c","tid":1466612,"uid":303858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:54:21.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔完美，可接受，但需要改善、改進。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"b64ad55ea8c4a5f7012b233195a1a5031271a06c","tid":1466612,"uid":303858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:54:33.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔完美，可接受，但需要改善、改進。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"ee85703eb4bc14248087e3ebcfc04883022bb530","tid":1466612,"uid":303858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:54:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔完美，可接受，但需要改善、改進。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"b028ac5303d278a9a52ea158e8b8b3c05a551a22","tid":1466612,"uid":303858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:54:55.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔完美，可接受，但需要改善、改進。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"7780ebd8c5de291d5453dfd80448368acac105e7","tid":1466612,"uid":303858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:55:06.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔完美，可接受，但需要改善、改進。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"ba4dcddcd18d966b4e74bcbcd264e38d8396ba94","tid":1466612,"uid":303858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:55:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: re